name: Tron Hero (Blue Hero)
description:
This is a 2 part collection 

“Everybody Nose”what the game is and how unforgiving it can be. My inspiration for the TRON shirt was that everyone wants to be in the game, but not everyone can navigate the game successfully. And when you become a casualty of the game, not I nor any of my SOS brethern will be able to assist you in your struggles. Stay on your grind. This shirt will be this 1st released in two colors. We have the Aqua blue edition for those makin the game work for them on the up & up, then we have the orange for our people who contrast the 9-5 and gotta live by that gutter grind. The design and art work were influenced by the movie TRON.

*the blue is darker in person
